<body>

<HeroNav theme="about" />

<section class="ex-hero">
  <img src="/images/fn/maternity_2.png" alt="Happy pregnant Indian mother &ndash; maternity care at Femme Nest" loading="eager" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high">
  <div class="ex-hero-content">
    <span class="ex-label">Our Expertise</span>
    <h1>Maternity Care</h1>
    <p>From your first trimester to your newborn's first breath &mdash; every moment gently held.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="ex-body">
  <p class="ex-intro">At Femme Nest, maternity care isn't just medical &mdash; it's an experience designed around you. Our dedicated team of obstetricians, midwives, and nurses walks beside you through every milestone, ensuring safety, comfort, and joy for both mother and baby.</p>

  <div class="ex-grid">
    <div class="ex-feature">
      <div class="ex-feature-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" width="26" height="26"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"/></svg></div>
      <h3>Prenatal Care</h3>
      <p>Comprehensive check-ups, ultrasounds, and wellness guidance through every trimester.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="ex-feature">
      <div class="ex-feature-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" width="26" height="26"><path d="M12 2a10 10 0 1 0 10 10"/><path d="M22 2 12 12"/></svg></div>
      <h3>Birthing Suites</h3>
      <p>Luxurious, home-like labour rooms with advanced monitoring and round-the-clock specialists.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="ex-feature">
      <div class="ex-feature-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" width="26" height="26"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 6v6l4 2"/></svg></div>
      <h3>24&times;7 Emergency</h3>
      <p>On-call obstetricians, anaesthetists, and neonatal teams ready at any hour.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="ex-feature">
      <div class="ex-feature-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" width="26" height="26"><path d="M12 2v20M2 12h20"/></svg></div>
      <h3>Postnatal Wellness</h3>
      <p>Lactation support, recovery programmes, and paediatric follow-ups for new mothers.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="ex-media">
    <img src="/images/fn/maternity_3.png" alt="Expecting mother at Femme Nest" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
    <div class="ex-media-caption">Every mother deserves the finest care &mdash; from the very first scan to the first breath.</div>
  </div>

  <div class="ex-details">
    <h2>A Complete Maternity Journey</h2>
    <p>Our maternity programme is thoughtfully structured around every phase &mdash; from preconception counselling to postnatal recovery. Each expectant mother is assigned a dedicated care coordinator who becomes her single point of contact throughout the journey.</p>
    <p>We combine the warmth of personalised care with the precision of modern medicine &mdash; advanced foetal monitoring, painless delivery options, and world-class operation theatres staffed by experienced consultants.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Preconception counselling</li>
      <li>High-risk pregnancy management</li>
      <li>Painless (epidural) delivery</li>
      <li>C-section & VBAC</li>
      <li>3D / 4D ultrasound imaging</li>
      <li>Lactation consulting</li>
      <li>Newborn screening</li>
      <li>Postnatal physiotherapy</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="ex-cta">
    <h2>Begin Your Journey With Us</h2>
    <p>Book a consultation with our maternity specialists today.</p>
    <a href="/#contact" class="ex-cta-btn">Book Appointment</a>
  </div>
</div>

<footer class="ex-foot">&copy; Femme Nest Hospital &middot; Care that feels like home</footer>

</body>
</html>



